\begin_layout Section
Feasibility
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Software
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Software libraries used will all be open source.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
GraphChi: To process graphs and perform algorithms to find communities.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
Cytoscape.js: JavaScript library for visualisation of communities found by
 GraphChi.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Hardware
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Users in the school have a 500MB storage limit on the network.
 For large graphs, more storage capacity will be needed in order to process
 the files.
 A request will be made to increase storage allowance to allow the analysis
 of these large graphs.
\end_layout

